\id MAL
\h Malachi
\mt1 Malachi
\toc1 Malachi
\toc2 Malachi
\c 3
\s1 PROPHET MALACHI
\p 
\v 1 Prophetangka Malachiangka Godumu kuku bamanda balkan, juma wanjarrmanka. Nyulu yalaman, “Godungku balkan, ‘Ngayu juma ngayku bama kukuji yungal, baral yanday-bunganka ngaykunku. Yinyamun bama ngaykundumun, yurranga Maja nyunguwunbu bayanba kaday. Nyulu ngayku promise kujil, yurra nyajinka.’” 
